To incorporate the GPS data with EKF

1. using `robot_localization` pkg
2. to configure `ekf_localization_node` and `navsat_transform_node` from (~/Downloads/robot_localization.pdf)
3. tutorials links: http://docs.ros.org/melodic/api/robot_localization/html/index.html
   https://github.com/methylDragon/ros-sensor-fusion-tutorial
   https://answers.ros.org/question/200071/how-to-fuse-imu-gps-using-robot_localization/
4. to check the performance of current implementation with ground truth